snippet.title: Stable Orbit – Launch Trailer (PC)
snippet.description:
Buy Now - https://www.greenmangaming.com/games/stable-orbit
Launching out of Early Access on September 27th

Space is dangerous. Survival is a challenge.
Design, build and control your own space station. Mission command and control is in your hands and only careful planning and vigilant supervision will keep your crew and space station safe. Manage scarce resources, survive a multitude of disasters and fund your station's growth by completing research projects.

Available on -
Steam - http://store.steampowered.com/app/481190/Stable_Orbit/
Green Man Gaming - https://www.greenmangaming.com/games/stable-orbit
Humble - https://www.humblebundle.com/store/stable-orbit

Archive footage courtesy of NASA. NASA do not endorse this product. 

Green Man Gaming Publishing - publisher of fine independent PC games. Games such as Aporia: Beyond The Valley, Stormworks: Build and Rescue, The Black Death, Stable Orbit, and much more.
